@startuml
actor "用户" as User
participant "浏览器" as UI
participant "Flask app.py" as App
participant "utils.py" as Utils
participant "qwen_service.py" as QwenService
database "SQLite" as DB
participant "千问 API" as Qwen

== 批量导入照片 ==
User -> UI: 选择或拖拽照片
UI -> App: POST /roll/{id}/upload
App -> Utils: save_photo_file()
Utils -> Utils: 保存原图并生成缩略图
Utils -> DB: 写入 photos
App --> UI: 返回导入结果

== AI 分析照片 ==
User -> UI: 点击 AI 分析
UI -> App: POST /photo/{id}/ai_analyze
App -> DB: 读取照片、胶卷、冲扫和标签
App -> QwenService: analyze_photo_with_qwen()
QwenService -> QwenService: 压缩图片
QwenService -> Qwen: 发送图片和上下文
Qwen --> QwenService: 描述、标签、评分建议
App -> DB: 更新照片 AI 字段和评分
App --> UI: 显示结果

== 生成索引图 ==
User -> UI: 点击生成胶片索引图
UI -> App: POST /roll/{id}/index_sheet
App -> Utils: generate_index_sheet()
Utils -> DB: 读取本卷照片
Utils -> Utils: 绘制底片袋风格高清 JPEG
Utils -> DB: 写入 index_sheets
App --> UI: 返回胶卷详情页
@enduml
